Class BirthInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • for_final_project.BirthInfo
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<BirthInfo>

    public class BirthInfo
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<BirthInfo>
    A BirthInfo object defines complete birthday information as a name plus a birthday, where the name is a Name object and birthday is a BirthDate object.
    Author:
    Kristin Jones
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
